org.dataconservancy.packaging.gui.view

Interface PackageMetadataView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    View<PackageMetadataPresenter>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PackageMetadataViewImpl

    public interface PackageMetadataView
extends View<PackageMetadataPresenter>
    The view that shows the package metadata screen. In this view, the user will be able to select a name for the package, select an ontology as well as put in other package specific metadata.
